    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Exactly what I needed! Thank you.\n\nThe correct answer is `item.cssClasses.item+= ' hide';` needed to be changed to `item.cssClasses.label += ' hide';`\n\nAlso, it doesnt like when a template is added.\n\n`templates: {\n                 item: facetTemplateCheckbox\n             }`\n\n`  var facetTemplateCheckbox =\n\n```\n   '<a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"facet-item\">' +\n     '<input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"{{cssClasses.checkbox}}\" value=\"{{name}}\" {{#isRefined}}checked{{/isRefined}} />{{name}}' +\n     '<span class=\"facet-count\">({{count}})</span>' +\n   '</a>';`\n```\n\nOther than that, works fine.\n",
    "created_at": "2016-02-22T18:23:25Z",
